 Chongryon officials and compatriots in Japan have always conducted patriotic activities full of conviction of victory in an alien land far away from the homeland, he said, adding: This is attributable to the great loving care and wise leadership of Kim Jong Il, who warmly embraces and shows deep love and care for Japan-resident Koreans as the same family members. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
