 Last year Kim Jong Il made sure that the 21st Congress of Chongryon, a landmark in the movement of Koreans in Japan in the new century, was brilliantly adorned as a congress of victors and unity. And he wisely led the struggle of Chongryon to definitely put its work on a new higher stage. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The reporter called upon Chongryon officials and Koreans in Japan to wage a more dynamic struggle to bring about a decisive turn in hewing out the work of Chongryon and the movement of Koreans in Japan in the new century in step with the stirring reality of the homeland of Juche which is advancing toward the high peak of a great prosperous powerful nation, closely rallied around Kim Jong Il. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
